latestIgtvVideos.title: Bikhri Aas Nikhri Preet!
latestIgtvVideos.caption: In the mood for Nostalgia, found this old video of my DD National show 'Bikhri Aas Nikhri Preet' Directed by the Late Lekh Tandon ji And Produced by KMPL...Some of you here might have seen this show... should be about 13yrs old? i look back at these moments as great learning blocks to make me the Actor i am today... Grateful!!! Also, Honestly i get embarrassed everytime i see this but i know i am better at lip sync coz of these experiences...So lets laugh at this!!!

latestIgtvVideos.title: Welcome to the world of 'Boon The Goon'
latestIgtvVideos.caption: Having some fun with my sister @akshitatiwary on her 21st bday... showing off a card trick i learnt from my dear friend @mirchi.arjun during this Quarantine period. I hope you guys enjoy it and it inspires you to learn something new during this period. Keep having fun with your family. Keep Chilling! We got this!!! #atkalockdown

latestIgtvVideos.title: Aao laut jaayein!
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
A song i had written about 15 yrs back came back to me in this Quarantine period!!! Thought of sharing it with everyone. It hopefully resonates with the idea of Halting our Big Strides,maybe Retreat a lil and let Life heal itself!!!
Would love to hear your versions or songs that you might have written.

#ATkaLockdown
